{"tid":1334804,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【荃灣武器庫】「香港民族陣綫」確認被捕男子為組織成員","createTime":"2019-07-20T09:04:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T09:38:02.000Z","uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4fde0e4b942fc760ba59f9b822cbfdd3467feb1e","tid":1334804,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:04:36.000Z","msg":"警方在荃灣一座工廠大廈的單位發現懷疑爆炸品，包括至少1公斤TATP烈性炸藥及10枚燃燒彈，一批武器及鏹水等，一名27歲男子涉嫌無牌管有爆炸品被捕。在警方檢獲的證物中，包括反對《逃犯條例》修例的單張及寫有「香港民族陣綫」的衣服。<br />\n<br />\n梁頌恆擔任發言人的支持港獨組織「香港民族陣綫」在社交網站表示，今日於荃灣工廠大廈被捕男子為該組織成員，已經有律師協助保釋。「香港民族陣綫」稱，據了解，該倉庫一直僅作為存放音響及其他宣傳物資之用，未知為何會有爆炸品在該單位當中。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，不排除有更多人被捕，正調查事件與證物標語上的組織有沒有關係。警方在單位搜獲TATP炸藥、10枚電油製成的燃燒彈，以及鏹水、刀、鐵棍、彈叉、頭盔、盔甲等等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1048741/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%BA%AB-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%99%A3%E7%B6%AB-%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%82%BA%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1048741%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AB-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F%25E9%2599%25A3%25E7%25B6%25AB-%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=75500951\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstd.stheadline.com%2Finstant%2Farticles%2Fdetail%2F1048741%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E8%258D%2583%25E7%2581%25A3%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E5%2599%25A8%25E5%25BA%25AB-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2597%258F%25E9%2599%25A3%25E7%25B6%25AB-%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2582%25BA%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1&h=22ff594c\" target=\"_blank\">http://std.stheadline.com/instant/articles/detail/1048741/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E8%8D%83%E7%81%A3%E6%AD%A6%E5%99%A8%E5%BA%AB-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%B0%91%E6%97%8F%E9%99%A3%E7%B6%AB-%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E7%82%BA%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1</a><br />\n<br />\n倉真係要有cctv , 以防俾人屈"},{"pid":"a9bbd8c5dd41ff745466b593ca2e67e187eb1d7b","tid":1334804,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"法庭：証據呢？<br />\n黑警：炸撚曬lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb1fe3c82843baa8fbb5fb4506340735ae54f3d4","tid":1334804,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:31:08.000Z","msg":"啤酒加毛巾就燃燒彈，<br />\n咁D餐廳咪全部都喺軍火庫？"},{"pid":"ad93cccaaa864100b07a0912e15e4dea2f342c1f","tid":1334804,"uid":165339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />民陣翻版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}